@node Source "DigiCam: The Source"

                                     Source
                                    --------

  The source is included, but it is still copyrighted.

  I included the source, because I probably will not do much to enhance it.
  Do a GUI or such is not on my plan. I have no need for it, I even had no
  such camera ...

  Anybody that wants to enhance the source is invited to do so as long he is
  republishing the result as freeware with source and my copyright note
  included.

  Commercial use of this source completly or in part is absolutely forbidden.

  A simple doubleclick on build should compile it on a proper installed SAS/C.

@endnode
